@node "Copyrights" "Copyrights"



			     @{b}Rights & Copyrights@{ub}



Difficult to say. In princip all trackers based on Karsten Obarskis SoundTracker
(commercial, 1986). But after all the Sound/Noise/ProTracker mutations these are
completly new programs. If you in order of right i think you  must  buy  an  old
Soundtracker.

	 @{i}On the view of the programmers of ProTracker the copyrights are:@{ui}

Protracker  V3.15  are  İ  1992-1993  Cryptoburners,  Version  3.61  İ1996   TEC
Design/RD10   (improvements)  and  are  FREEWARE.  For  additional  Cryptoburner
copyrights read his docs. Any payment and distribution what are over  the  costs
of  5  DM per unit is strictly prohibited. Protracker is not an commercial tool!
The distributors of the @{fg shine}AMINET @{fg text}serie, @{fg shine}Fred  Fish
@{fg  text}and  all bulletin boards who works without payement have the right to
spread this package without request.

@endnode

