@node "Install" "Install"

This is only an update of the basic Protracker files. An excellent PT Manual you
will  find  in Aminet/MUS/EDIT from Hċvard Pedersen if you are need help for the
usage.

					How install this package:

	Use the included installerscript and make an Assign ST-00: to your
	music drawer. If you want to install manually, here some hints:



	Copy all files from the s drawer to s: from your harddisk. There are:

	-pt.help
	The PT Online Help if you press Help

	-pt.keymap
	If in S:, the german keyboard driver. If not here,
	the standart US map is used. For other languages
	(easy to change, simply use an HEX Editor and change
	your keycodes you wish.)

	-PLST
	loaded and saved in S:, your Sample list for PED/PLST

	-pt.config-00
	The main config, was loaded by start. If not aviable,
	PT use the internal standart configuration.

	Protracker
	The Tracker Mainfile, copy anywhere.

	libs:
	xpkmaster.library/powerpacker.library needed
	(not included) for depacking/packing Modules.

	Please ensure that you created an drawer who included the follow directories:
	modules
	songs
	samples
	Add an assign 'ST-00' to this drawer.


		(Sorry, but this is an UPDATE).

@endnode
